<html>
<body>

<p>
<%= @request.requester.name %> wants to add you as a friend. 
</p>

<% if @request.message and @request.message != '' %>
<p>"<%= @request.message %>"</p>
<% end %>

<p>
Having friends in tourb.us makes it easy to
track what shows your friends are going to and are a great way to
find out about shows you might enjoy. 
</p>

<p>
To <strong>accept</strong> this request <a href="<%= @confirm_url %>">click here</a>.<br/>
To <strong>deny</strong> this request <a href="<%= @deny_url %>">click here</a>.<br/><br/>
You may need to log in before confirming or denying the request.

</p>

<p>
You can manage all of your outstanding <a href="<%= @friend_requests_url %>">friend requests here</a>.
</p>

<p>
<%= @email_signoff %>
</p>
</body>
</html>
  
